### Delete full submission (manager-only)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/v1/submissions/{{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer <manager-token>


### Clear only schedule (manager-only)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/v1/submissions/{{studentId}}/schedule
Authorization: Bearer <manager-token>


### Get submission (for verification)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/submissions/{{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer <manager-token>
